  </h1>

  <h4>
    Layboka AI helps eCommerce brands convert visitors into buyers using AI-powered conversations, checkout assistance, abandoned cart recovery and real-time sales automation.
  </h4>

</section>

<section class="section">

  <div class="grid">

    <div class="card">

      <div class="icon">🤖</div>

      <h3>AI Sales Assistant</h3>

      <p>
        Our AI chatbot talks to customers 24/7, recommends products, answers questions and boosts conversions automatically.
      </p>

    </div>

    <div class="card">

      <div class="icon">🛒</div>

      <h3>Checkout Recovery</h3>

      <p>
        Recover abandoned carts with automated WhatsApp messages, email follow-ups and smart checkout reminders.
      </p>

    </div>

    <div class="card">

      <div class="icon">📈</div>

      <h3>Conversion Growth</h3>

      <p>
        Turn your Shopify traffic into revenue with personalized AI conversations designed to increase order value and sales.
      </p>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<footer>

  <div class="footer-grid">

    <div class="footer-box">
      <h3>Layboka AI</h3>
      <a href="index.html">Home</a>
      <a href="pricing.html">Pricing</a>
      <a href="dashboard.html">Dashboard</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-box">
      <h3>Company</h3>
      <a href="about.html">About</a>
      <a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
      <a href="privacy.html">Privacy</a>
      <a href="terms.html">Terms</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-box">
      <h3>Features</h3>
      <a href="#">AI Chatbot</a>
      <a href="#">Recovery System</a>
      <a href="#">Analytics</a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="copyright">
    © 2026 Layboka AI • All Rights Reserved
  </div>

</footer>

<script>

function toggleMenu(){
  document.getElementById("nav").classList.toggle("show");
}

</script>

</body>
</html>
